93ec48f [svn] Refactor and quote % characters in `svn_prompt_info` - c76dc91 [svn] Return true repo name in `svn_get_repo_name` - 75ed59b [svn-fast-info] Quote % characters in svn branch name - ef3a85c [svn-fast-info] URL-decode svn branch name - 4e777ef [trapd00r] Fix potential command injection in `zsh_path` - a7c46d0 [ubuntu] Fix `defining function based on alias` error (#10560) - 805427e [updater] Give priority to `zstyle` settings if set (#10587) - 3e9fe6e [virtualenv] Quote % in `virtualenv_prompt_info` - 93cea53 [yarn] Update completion (#10579)
Documentation:
- 4e2f4cd [vi-mode] Fix link typo in readme (#10570)

- d3bb52d Style: Declare globals properly - 67cc59b Style: Some code style fixes - fbdc078 Style: Use 24bit colors in Oh My Zsh logo if supported - 567bd59 [cli] Refactor: Use self-referencing in subcommand functions - c63ba17 [installer] Refactor: Simplify `user_can_sudo` check - 7ae4f76 [kubectl] Refactor: Optimize completion generation - 596cef8 [svn-fast-info] Style: Fix code style and `svn info` locale - bddecfe [updater] Style: Remove statl from `git pull`
